data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. PRICED REDUCED! SELLER IS MOTIVATED! This beautiful spacious, single-family home is partially furnished, it features 3-bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms. Master bath includes a garden tub and a separate shower. Kitchen comes with stainless steel appliances, new garbage disposal. Pool table in the two-car garage will remain in the property. Garage door is new. The private inground has been resurfaced 2 years ago and pump is a year young. Pool is fully enclosed patio furniture is included, The deck is extremely spacious. great for friends and family entertainment. Irrigation system has been recently rewired. The roof is 5 years young, This property is located in Southern Dunes community; which offers 24 hour security, playground, community pool, fitness center and a fabulous golf course. This home is located near many conveniences. Near HWY 27, I4, Posner Park strip mall. several dining area, banks, walking distance to Walmart, Winn-Dixie and more. Must see to appreciate.
